<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/ROBOLUTION_ICON.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <title>ROBOLUTION 2023 Registration</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --navy: #0a2463;
            --navy-light: #1e3a8a;
            --navy-dark: #051c5f;
            --accent: #3e92cc;
            --light-bg: #f8f9fa;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --light-gray: #e9ecef;
            --text-dark: #212529;
            --text-light: #6c757d;
            --success: #28a745;
            --danger: #dc3545;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--light-bg);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: var(--white);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: var(--navy);
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--navy);
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .header p {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        .section {
            background-color: var(--light-bg);
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--navy);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .section:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .section-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--navy);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .section-title::before {
            content: "";
            display: inline-block;
            width: 8px;
            height: 18px;
            background-color: var(--accent);
            margin-right: 10px;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--navy);
        }
        
        input[type="text"],
        input[type="email"],
        input[type="password"],
        textarea,
        select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transition: border 0.3s ease;
            font-family: inherit;
        }
        
        input[type="text"]:focus,
        input[type="email"]:focus,
        input[type="password"]:focus,
        textarea:focus,
        select:focus {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(62, 146, 204, 0.2);
        }
        
        .checkbox-group {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .checkbox-label, .radio-label {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }
        
        .checkbox-label:hover, .radio-label:hover {
            background-color: rgba(62, 146, 204, 0.1);
        }
        
        .checkbox-label input, .radio-label input {
            margin-right: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .radio-group {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .required {
            color: var(--danger);
            margin-left: 3px;
        }
        
        .note {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-style: italic;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        .btn-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .btn {
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--navy);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: var(--navy-light);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #d1d7dc;
        }
        
        .btn-danger {
            background-color: var(--danger);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-danger:hover {
            background-color: #bd2130;
        }
        
        .privacy-policy {
            background-color: var(--light-bg);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
        }
        
        .privacy-policy h3 {
            color: var(--navy);
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        
        .payment-options {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .payment-option {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: calc(50% - 10px);
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: var(--white);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .payment-option:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .payment-option h3 {
            color: var(--navy);
            margin-top: 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--light-gray);
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .file-upload {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .file-upload input[type="file"] {
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: var(--light-bg);
            border: 1px dashed #ccc;
            border-radius: 4px;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        .error-message {
            color: var(--danger);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1);
            border-radius: 4px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--danger);
        }
        
        a {
            color: var(--accent);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        
        a:hover {
            color: var(--navy);
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        /* Responsive adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .payment-options {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .payment-option {
                width: 100%;
            }
            
            .btn-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }
            
            .btn {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>FINAL-REGISTRATION ROBOLUTION 2025</h1>
            <p>ðŸ”¥ ROBOTICS & AUTOMATION COMPETITION INTERNATIONAL 2025 ðŸ”¥</p>
        </div>
        
        <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined') { %>
            <div class="error-message"><%= error %></div>
        <% } %>
        
        <form action="/register" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">Event Information</div>
                <p>The mechanics of the competition will be adopted the Robotics Championship International Competition, Oradea, Romania, the Virtual Robot Simulator (VRS) of Illinois, US, and the Robosim (ZMRobo) of China, and our partners from Mexico, East Africa, Thailand, Hongkong, Malaysia, India, Japan, and other countries will also participate.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>SEMINAR & WORKSHOP</li>
                    <li>EXHIBITS</li>
                    <li>CERTIFICATIONS</li>
                    <li>COMPETITION</li>
                </ul>
                <p>FREE registration for ROBOSIM, ZMROBO Innovative Challenge, E-ROBOT, & FREE-Style Virtual Robot Simulator (VRS), and Cyber ROBO Challenge Category!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">Personal Information</div>
                <p class="note">Fill-up the following. Note: Do not use all Capital Letters (Example: JUAN DELA CRUZ)</p>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="fullname">Fullname (Complete Name) <span class="required">*</span></label>
                    <input type="text" id="fullname" name="fullname" required>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="teamMembers">TEAM MEMBERS' NAMES (if you have)</label>
                    <textarea id="teamMembers" name="teamMembers" rows="3"></textarea>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>CATEGORY <span class="required">*</span></label>
                    <div class="radio-group">
                        <div class="radio-label">
                            <input type="radio" id="elementary" name="category" value="Elementary">
                            <label for="elementary">Elementary</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="radio-label">
                            <input type="radio" id="highschool" name="category" value="Highschool">
                            <label for="highschool">Highschool</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="radio-label">
                            <input type="radio" id="college" name="category" value="College/Post-Graduate/Industry">
                            <label for="college">College/Post-Graduate / Industry Practitioner (Adult)</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="school">School Name/ Company/Business</label>
                    <input type="text" id="school" name="school">
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="address">Home Address <span class="required">*</span></label>
                    <input type="text" id="address" name="address" required>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Email Address <span class="required">*</span></label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                    <p class="note">Please enter a valid email address (e.g., example@domain.com)</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">COMPETITION (Optional)</div>
                <p>For Mechanics, here is the link <a href="https://bit.ly/RobolutionMechanics" target="_blank">https://bit.ly/RobolutionMechanics</a></p>
                <p>(EROBOT category - Erovoutika robot should be used)</p>
                
                <div class="checkbox-group">
                    <% if (typeof categories !== 'undefined' && categories.length > 0) { %>
                        <% categories.forEach(function(cat) { %>
                            <div class="checkbox-label">
                                <input type="checkbox" id="cat-<%= cat._id %>" name="competition[]" value="<%= cat.title %>">
                                <label for="cat-<%= cat._id %>"><%= cat.title %></label>
                            </div>
                        <% }); %>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <!-- Default options if no categories are available -->
                        <div class="checkbox-label">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="freestyle-hs" name="competition[]" value="FREE-STYLE-HS">
                            <label for="freestyle-hs">FREE-STYLE (INNOVATIVE PROJECTS) - HIGH SCHOOL/SENIOR HS CATEGORY</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="checkbox-label">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="erobot-hs" name="competition[]" value="E-ROBOT-HS">
                            <label for="erobot-hs">E-ROBOT: LINE FOLLOWING CLASSIC - HIGH SCHOOL/SENIOR HS CATEGORY</label>
                        </div>
                    <% } %>
                    
                    <!-- Always include the "Other" option -->
                    <div class="checkbox-label">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="other-comp" name="competition[]" value="OTHER">
                        <label for="other-comp">Other:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="other-comp-text" name="other_competition" style="width: 300px; margin-left: 10px;">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">International SEMINAR & WORKSHOP per head <span class="required">*</span></div>
                
                <div class="checkbox-group">
                    <div class="checkbox-label">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="seminar-only" name="workshop[]" value="SEMINAR">
                        <label for="seminar-only">SEMINAR (Php 195) - 1 certificate per head - morning only</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="checkbox-label">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="seminar-robotics" name="workshop[]" value="SEMINAR-ROBOTICS">
                        <label for="seminar-robotics">SEMINAR & WORKSHOP-ROBOTICS TRACK (Php 395) - 2 certificates - morning & afternoon</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="checkbox-label">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="seminar-ict" name="workshop[]" value="SEMINAR-ICT">
                        <label for="seminar-ict">SEMINAR & WORKSHOP- ICT (Php 390) - 2 certificates - morning & afternoon</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="checkbox-label">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="foreign" name="workshop[]" value="FOREIGN">
                        <label for="foreign">Foreign Participants - 10 dollars</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="checkbox-label">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="professional" name="workshop[]" value="PROFESSIONAL">
                        <label for="professional">Professional Teachers/ Electronics Engineers/Electrical Engineer with CPD points- P450</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="checkbox-label">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="other-workshop" name="workshop[]" value="OTHER">
                        <label for="other-workshop">Other:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="other-workshop-text" name="other_workshop" style="width: 300px; margin-left: 10px;">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">FOR IECEP MANILA & LAGUNA, & UMAK ONLY</div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="code">Please type your code</label>
                    <input type="text" id="code" name="code">
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">PAYMENT OPTIONS</div>
                <div class="payment-options">
                    <div class="payment-option">
                        <h3>SECURITY BANK</h3>
                        <p>0000021660817</p>
                        <p>EROVOUTIKA ENTERPRISE</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="payment-option">
                        <h3>GCASH</h3>
                        <p>09061497307</p>
                        <p>BHAI DEPLOMO</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="payment">For SEMINAR & WORKSHOP: Upload your payment <span class="required">*</span></label>
                    <div class="file-upload">
                        <input type="file" id="payment" name="payment" accept="image/*,.pdf">
                        <p class="note">Upload 1 supported file. Max 10 MB.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="payment_details">For SEMINAR & WORKSHOP: Type the amount & Reference number</label>
                    <input type="text" id="payment_details" name="payment_details">
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="privacy-policy">
                <h3>Privacy Policy</h3>
                <p>Erovoutika ("we" or "us") values its visitors' privacy. This privacy policy summarizes what information we might collect from a registered user or another visitor and what we will and will not do with it.</p>
                <p>Please note that this privacy policy does not govern the collection and use of information by companies that Erovoutika does not control, nor by individuals not employed or managed by Erovoutika. If you visit a Web site that we mention or link to, be sure to review its privacy policy before providing the site with information.</p>
                
                <div class="checkbox-group">
                    <div class="checkbox-label">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="privacy" name="privacy_agree" value="1" required>
                        <label for="privacy">I agree to the Erovoutika Privacy Policy <span class="required">*</span></label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="btn-container">
                
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit Registration</button>
                <button type="reset" class="btn btn-danger">Clear Form</button>
            </div>
        </form>
        
        <div class="section" style="margin-top: 30px;">
            <div class="section-title">FREE SERIES ONLINE TRAINING</div>
            <p>Series FREE Training Registration Link: <a href="https://bit.ly/TrainingSeriesRobo" target="_blank">https://bit.ly/TrainingSeriesRobo</a></p>
            
            <div class="section-title" style="margin-top: 20px;">For any concern, you may message us in our Facebook Page:</div>
            <p><a href="https://www.facebook.com/robolution2019" target="_blank">https://www.facebook.com/robolution2019</a> or <a href="https://www.facebook.com/erovoutika" target="_blank">https://www.facebook.com/erovoutika</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <script src="/js/registration.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
